OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1776341451
OL,3,CPolice investigating bridge incident
OL,4,Cname man who entered water
OL,6,FPolice investigating an incident on a
OL,7,Fbridge over the River Tyne have
OL,8,Fconfirmed the identity of a man who
OL,9,Fentered the water.
OL,11,FOfficers received a report of a man
OL,12,Fentering the water from the Redheugh
OL,13,FBridge, in Gateshead, shortly before
OL,14,F10pm on Friday (10 April).
OL,16,FIt was first reported that a group of
OL,17,Fpeople had been involved in an
OL,18,Faltercation ` where a man had later
OL,19,Fentered the water.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1776341451
OL,3,CPolice investigating bridge incident
OL,4,Cname man who entered water
OL,6,FEnquiries have since established that
OL,7,Fthe man had left the scene of the
OL,8,Faltercation before entering the water
OL,9,Fa short time later.
OL,11,FNorthumbria Police said since the
OL,12,Freport, extensive enquiries have been
OL,13,Fcarried out in an effort to locate the
OL,14,Fman ` who can now be named as 39-year-
OL,15,Fold Dean Larvin, from Gateshead.
OL,17,FHe has not yet been found, and Mr
OL,18,FLarvin's family continue to be
OL,19,Fsupported by officers.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1776341451
OL,3,CPolice investigating bridge incident
OL,4,Cname man who entered water
OL,6,FAs part of the initial stages of the
OL,7,Finvestigation, a 48-year-old-woman was
OL,8,Farrested in connection with the
OL,9,Fincident. She has since been released
OL,10,Fon police bail pending further
OL,11,Fenquiries.
OL,13,FLeading the investigation, Detective
OL,14,FInspector Ash Loader from the Force's
OL,15,FMajor Investigation Team, said: "Our
OL,16,Fefforts to find Dean are very much
OL,17,Fongoing, however it is not possible to
OL,18,Fprovide any timescales around locating
OL,19,Fhim.
OL,26,@wD@aOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1776341451
OL,3,CPolice investigating bridge incident
OL,4,Cname man who entered water
OL,6,F"Thank you to our colleagues and
OL,7,Fpartner agencies who continue to
OL,8,Fprovide us with support as our search
OL,9,Factivity continues."
OL,11,FOfficers continue to appeal for any
OL,12,Fwitnesses who may have been in the
OL,13,Farea at the time, especially those who
OL,14,Fmay have dashcam footage of the
OL,15,Fmoments surrounding the incident.
OL,17,FAnyone with information should contact
OL,18,Fthe force on 101.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@TO]
